'''Ursu Aberkan''' ([[assaɣ usnan]]: ''Ursus americanus''), d d yiwet n [[Talmest|telmest]] deg [[taswit(tasnudert)|tewsit]] n [[Ursu]] yeṭṭafaren [[tawacult]] n [[timellalin|tɣelɣalin]] yittidiren deg [[Marikan n Ugafa]]. Ɣas ma yella semman-as aberkan, tikkal nezmer ad naff [[ini]]-ynes yedda ɣer [[ademdam|udemdam]], [[aras]] neɣ Tikwal d [[aẓerwal]]. Ursu-a d ameẓyan deg [[tiddi]] ma nwala waytmaten-is niḍen (am w[[ursu aras]] neɣ [[Ursu Amellal]]), imi [[tiddi]]-ynes tettaweṭ ar 1,80 m deg teɣzi, ma d [[azuk]] azal n 70kg.

